      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in showroom condition. This vehicle has been treated with the utmost care by a single enthusiast owner and currently shows only 12,000 miles. The Carrara White Metallic exterior is absolutely flawless, featuring a professional ceramic coating that provides a deep, glass-like luster; there are no stone chips, scratches, or door dings to be found. The interior is equally immaculate, with the Black leather upholstery remaining supple and free of any wear or creasing, still retaining its original factory scent. All onboard technology, including the PCM navigation and premium Bose audio system, operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in 'as-new' condition, supported by a meticulous service history performed exclusively at authorized Porsche centers. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never been driven in inclement weather or on a track. This is a rare, investment-grade example that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
